This is a placeholder for the new WilnBill logo PNG file.
The SVG version has been created at install/img/logo.svg
You can convert the SVG to PNG using an online converter or image editing software.

Logo features:
- Modern WiFi signal icon with gradient
- "WilnBill" text in bold
- "Modern WiFi Billing" tagline
- Purple gradient colors (#667eea to #764ba2)
- Clean, minimalist design
